There is no path to a majority government. One option would be to tolerate a broad bourgeois government, without cabinet participation from the <span style="color: #c00000;">**DEM**</span> at all. This is the only viable option for a government, as the bourgeois parties refuse to cooperate with us in any other capacity.

Otherwise, new elections have to be called, where the extremist parties stand to gain.

